OL,3,CScientists make new discovery about
OL,4,Cthe history of the Giant's Causeway
OL,6,FScientists have made a new discovery
OL,7,Fabout the history of the Giant's
OL,8,FCauseway rock formation.
OL,10,FNew research has revealed that
OL,11,FNorthern Ireland's volcanic past,
OL,12,Fwhich created the Causeway's
OL,13,Fdistinctive 40,000 basalt columns,
OL,14,Fhappened over a much shorter period
OL,15,Fthan previously thought.
OL,17,FIt was discovered that volcanic events
OL,18,Faround the region formed rocks,
OL,19,Fincluding the Causeway, in just 5.5
OL,20,Fmillion years ` eight million years
OL,21,Fless than previous estimates.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
