CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1781486246
OL,3,CScientists make new discovery about
OL,4,Cthe history of the Giant's Causeway
OL,6,FThe Giant's Causeway's distinctive
OL,7,Flandscape was formed during intense
OL,8,Fvolcanic activity which forced molten
OL,9,Frock up through cracks in the earth.
OL,11,FThick lava flows then cooled,
OL,12,Fcontracted and cracked, creating about
OL,13,F40,000 basalt columns.
OL,15,FDr Tapster said the cutting-edge
OL,16,Fresearch by the Geological Survey of
OL,17,FNorthern Ireland (GSNI) and the BGS,
OL,18,Fhas reconstructed a new timeline for
OL,19,Fvolcanic activity across Northern
OL,20,FIreland.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1781486246
OL,3,CScientists make new discovery about
OL,4,Cthe history of the Giant's Causeway
OL,6,FIt has allowed researchers to place
OL,7,Fthe volcanic activity that led to the
OL,8,Fformation of the Giant's Causeway
OL,9,Fwithin a much more precise global
OL,10,Fcontext for the first time.
OL,12,FThe research has significantly updated
OL,13,Fthe understanding of when specific
OL,14,Fvolcanic events happened in Northern
OL,15,FIreland.
OL,17,FAs a result, scientists can more
OL,18,Fconfidently connect those events to
OL,19,Factivity and landmarks elsewhere,
OL,20,Fincluding Scotland.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
