FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1781486246
OL,3,CScientists make new discovery about
OL,4,Cthe history of the Giant's Causeway
OL,6,FIt also connects the processes that
OL,7,Fcaused the development of the Giant's
OL,8,FCauseway to a globally significant
OL,9,Fvolcanic event seen in rocks as far
OL,10,Faway as Greenland about 60 million
OL,11,Fyears ago.
OL,13,FThe first lava flows of Northern
OL,14,FIreland's Antrim Plateau previously
OL,15,Fwere thought to have occurred millions
OL,16,Fof years before the Staffa basalts and
OL,17,Fthe formation of Fingal's Cave, but
OL,18,Fthey can now be connected much more
OL,19,Fdefinitively as part of the same
OL,20,Fvolcanic activity.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
