PN,30806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1781486246
OL,3,CScientists make new discovery about
OL,4,Cthe history of the Giant's Causeway
OL,6,FResearchers said it is the same for
OL,7,Fthe Giant's Causeway with formations
OL,8,Fon Rum, the Mourne Mountains, and
OL,9,Fmagmatism in Skye.
OL,11,FDr Tapster said; "By looking at the
OL,12,Ftimescales and the high resolution
OL,13,Ftimeline, we're able to match it up
OL,14,Fwith various other locations,
OL,15,Fparticularly in the Inner Hebrides in
OL,16,FScotland, the volcanics of Mull, Rum,
OL,17,Fthe Isle of Skye, and taking a bigger
OL,18,Fview, looking at Greenland and the
OL,19,FFaroe Islands."
OL,26,@sD@ROU{D@OO]
