OL,3,CScientists make new discovery about
OL,4,Cthe history of the Giant's Causeway
OL,6,FThe research is part of a wider
OL,7,Finitiative at the British Geological
OL,8,FSurvey to improve the understanding of
OL,9,Fthe UK's geology through better
OL,10,Fquantifying geological time in the
OL,11,Frocks around us.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/7
